Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.60,0:01:42.47,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要去斯卡布羅集市嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.85,0:01:49.58,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}歐芹 鼠尾草 迷迭香和百里香
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.99,0:01:56.59,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請代我向住在那裡的一個人問好…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.05,0:01:58.32,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原來是奏人君啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.57,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊 唯小姐
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.08,0:02:05.46,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夜色真美啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.11,0:02:09.03,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你為什麼要坐在那種地方呢
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.90,0:02:10.68,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很危險的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.31,0:02:12.68,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒事的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.90,0:02:15.12,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 真的很危險啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.07,0:02:21.96,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你臉上又是害怕又是焦躁的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.99,0:02:25.05,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的是 非常可愛
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.67,0:02:30.27,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其實我最討厭你那種表情了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.03,0:02:34.35,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想著 為什麼你會怕我
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.65,0:02:36.38,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這會讓我很不安
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.17,0:02:38.87,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現…現在不是的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.44,0:02:42.20,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為奏人君你好像快掉下去了 我才會害怕…
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.07,0:02:47.10,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}反正你是不會知道
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.64,0:02:50.69,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}自己有多自以為是吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.78,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}愚蠢至極
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.54,0:02:59.59,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蠢得讓人發笑 這點也讓人覺得可愛
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.78,0:03:03.00,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不可以擔心你嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.27,0:03:05.52,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對我來說那是毫無用處的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.17,0:03:08.93,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.22,0:03:13.04,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你那麼想要我從這兒下來嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.04,0:03:17.72,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼 吻我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.99,0:03:22.70,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果你願意吻我的話 我下來也無妨
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.16,0:03:27.51,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果你說不要的話
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.48,0:03:32.00,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就請你不要管我 趕緊消失吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.22,0:03:33.79,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.06,0:03:42.80,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.28,0:03:46.15,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你居然當真了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.34,0:03:52.24,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果真是個無可救藥的笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.54,0:03:55.97,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我下來就是了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.24,0:03:57.76,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊 真的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.86,0:03:58.32,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.14,0:04:01.81,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奏 奏人君
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.09,0:04:06.47,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼 再見了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.01,0:04:07.52,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誒
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.18,0:04:21.07,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奏人君
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.48,0:04:22.32,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你沒事吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.18,0:04:25.54,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奏人君 奏人君
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.08,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你好煩啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.76,0:04:31.16,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過是從二樓掉下來
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.54,0:04:34.68,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你覺得我會有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.09,0:04:35.63,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.01,0:04:39.96,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果這樣就能死的話倒是輕鬆不少
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.23,0:04:43.85,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想死…嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.69,0:04:48.40,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}話雖如此 不過不是現在
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.62,0:04:56.62,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對了 我有個很中意的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.84,0:05:00.98,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天就破例帶唯小姐過去
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.04,0:05:09.85,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這些是
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.50,0:05:12.42,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如你所見 是蠟像
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.18,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我還是第一次看見
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.21,0:05:19.10,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}泰迪一來這裡心情就會變得很好
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.10,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對吧 泰迪
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.43,0:05:26.73,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看起來不怎麼開心啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.89,0:05:30.68,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我總覺得蠟像有點恐怖
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.98,0:05:34.17,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}像泰迪那麼可愛的倒還好
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.79,0:05:38.90,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我當然知道泰迪是最可愛的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.72,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過 從已經「失去靈魂」
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.85,0:05:46.18,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這層意思上看 泰迪也是一樣的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.53,0:05:48.40,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「失去靈魂」？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.27,0:05:55.41,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}若你變成{\rTEXT-CN-RED\blur2}無法言語的屍體{\r\blur2} 會何等美麗呢
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.97,0:05:56.35,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誒
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.73,0:06:01.11,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想不想變成人偶 現在 就在這裡
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.28,0:06:02.66,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奏 奏人君
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.93,0:06:04.93,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我會精心裝扮你
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.25,0:06:08.09,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.99,0:06:13.21,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}泰迪也一定會因為有了新伙伴而高興的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.02,0:06:18.16,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對唯小姐而言 也沒有什麼損失吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.83,0:06:19.91,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.13,0:06:25.92,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我絕對不想…成為人偶
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.44,0:06:37.04,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你為什麼要那麼害怕呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.47,0:06:40.80,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過 真是不錯的表情啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.64,0:06:42.37,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.96,0:06:45.80,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真不錯啊 這個表情
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.15,0:06:48.10,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是漂亮極了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.02,0:06:54.19,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因恐懼而扭曲的表情 為什麼會這麼誘人呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.00,0:06:56.62,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.49,0:07:00.44,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奏人君 我求求你
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.57,0:07:01.44,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快住手
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.55,0:07:07.07,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}讓我把你這張煩人的嘴完美地縫合起來吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.12,0:07:07.53,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誒
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.26,0:07:11.21,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我會在你的眼睛裡鑲入玻璃珠
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.88,0:07:13.67,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什麼顏色好呢
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.34,0:07:17.83,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因鮮血盡失而變得晶瑩通透的肌膚
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.27,0:07:22.92,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}會變得像陶瓷一樣潔白光滑吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.50,0:07:35.63,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我會好好喝乾你的血的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.39,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請不用擔心
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.88,0:07:43.48,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你一定會比任何新娘都美麗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.61,0:07:48.40,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這 這些蠟像 難道是…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.35,0:07:50.65,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒錯
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.76,0:07:54.11,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她們就是那些{\rTEXT-CN-RED\blur2}祭品新娘
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.82,0:08:00.20,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}馬上就會讓你覺得舒服的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.28,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好難…受
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.10,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奏人
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.43,0:08:16.73,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}憐司叫你
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.48,0:08:20.54,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好麻煩啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.27,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}綾人君
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.25,0:08:28.63,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}謝…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.47,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別誤會
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.42,0:08:37.96,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天沒什麼興致
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.48,0:08:41.45,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好累
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.36,0:08:55.11,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昴君
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.93,0:09:02.98,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 要是繼續待在這裡的話 必死無疑
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.66,0:09:07.66,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是…我也沒辦法…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.24,0:09:13.21,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在的話…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.94,0:09:17.43,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誒…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.30,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果是現在的話…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.89,0:09:47.30,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然 我還是想知道真相
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.90,0:09:55.79,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昴君
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.55,0:10:01.93,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你沒有逃走嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.23,0:10:05.83,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這種機會可是很難得的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.94,0:10:07.64,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.40,0:10:12.08,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果你知道關於我父親的事 就請告訴我
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.43,0:10:17.68,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們說我是教會獻出的祭品
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.11,0:10:19.68,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.80,0:10:32.28,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誒？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.42,0:10:40.05,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果用這把銀製匕首刺進我們吸血鬼的胸口
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.94,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就能置我們於死地
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.08,0:10:44.54,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誒 為什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.82,0:10:55.47,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請拿著它
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.82,0:10:58.42,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請寸不離身地拿好它
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.12,0:11:01.42,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吶 快殺了他 殺了他啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.15,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要我殺死誰啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.23,0:11:06.61,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 你究竟是在對誰說話
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.53,0:11:09.24,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在向誰求助啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.96,0:11:03.10,TEXT-CN(UP),,0,0,0,,{\blur2}求求你快殺了他
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.75,0:11:06.96,TEXT-CN(UP),,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放我走吧 求求你 放我走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.72,0:11:12.92,TEXT-CN(UP),,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果做不到的話 你一定要用這把匕首刺穿我的心臟
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.13,0:11:12.46,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的眼中映著的 究竟是誰
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.92,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是個溫柔的孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.60,0:11:18.46,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 我會殺死你的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.33,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是你的願望吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.44,0:11:25.44,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一定會幫你實現它的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.93,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小賤人 我都等得不耐煩了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.45,0:11:34.26,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禮人君
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.72,0:11:36.91,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.10,0:11:38.91,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}露出那副表情
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.10,0:11:41.89,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出去
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.54,0:11:47.33,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是認真的嗎 小賤人
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.92,0:11:53.60,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昴君的匕首啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.69,0:12:00.20,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要做什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.10,0:12:05.94,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真榮幸啊 沒想到你愛我那麼深
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.75,0:12:07.21,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誒
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.94,0:12:13.40,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對於吸血鬼而言 殺死對方便是至高的愛的告白
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.51,0:12:20.74,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是為那些可謂擁有永恒生命的人們所落下的帷幕
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.79,0:12:23.50,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禮…禮人君？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.77,0:12:26.15,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你可能不明白吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.44,0:12:29.53,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那種愛越深恨越切的感覺
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.58,0:12:35.34,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們啊 歸根結底是相似的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.26,0:12:40.62,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你炙熱的鮮血散發著極致的香氣 低聲訴求著
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.62,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禮人君 放開我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.65,0:12:46.90,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道你在渴求著我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.14,0:12:50.06,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在說什麼啊 請你放開我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.55,0:12:54.28,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說吧 喊出來吧 說你想要我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.31,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神並不存在
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.82,0:12:59.77,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你也不需要遵守規則
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.50,0:13:05.34,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}壓抑隱藏自己的欲望生活 有意義嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.02,0:13:10.48,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有什麼意義…我不知道
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.62,0:13:16.22,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.60,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我相信
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.41,0:13:24.52,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不論發生多麼痛苦的事 我都會相信
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.80,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為人類很脆弱
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.83,0:13:29.77,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以才要去相信
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.46,0:13:41.92,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}像小賤人這樣的人 我還是第一次遇到呢
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.62,0:13:45.30,TEXT-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}之前只對你的血感興趣
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.33,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過我改主意了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.10,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你所喜愛的東西
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.67,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那雙瞳中倒映的一切
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.40,0:14:40.35,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}除我以外的世界都沉入黑暗吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.35,0:14:44.90,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為 你需要注視的就只有我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.66,0:14:50.26,TEXT-CN-RED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}讓我來把你弄壞吧
